OL,3,CLollipop people will return to
OL,4,CScottish town after local campaign
OL,6,FCrossing patrols will be temporarily
OL,7,Freinstated on Queen Street in Castle
OL,8,FDouglas after a local campaign.
OL,10,FIn October, ITV Border reported that a
OL,11,Fpetition had been set up by residents
OL,12,Fafter the council announced it would
OL,13,Fpull the roll of a lollipop person in
OL,14,Fa bid to curb spending.
OL,16,FThe petition has gained more than four
OL,17,Fhundred signatures.
