OL,3,CLollipop people will return to
OL,4,CScottish town after local campaign
OL,6,FFollowing an independent safety review
OL,7,Fof the pedestrian crossing, a series
OL,8,Fof upgrades will be carried out to
OL,9,Fimprove visibility and accessibility.
OL,11,FThese will take place during the
OL,12,FEaster and Summer school holidays.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Dumfries and
OL,15,FGalloway Council said: "A crossing
OL,16,Fpatrol will be reinstated on a
OL,17,Ftemporary basis at the crossing from
OL,18,FMonday 9 February. This is being
OL,19,Fprovided by the council's Streetscene
OL,20,FTeam and will be in place until the
OL,21,Fimprovement works are carried out"
