OL,3,CLollipop people will return to
OL,4,CScottish town after local campaign
OL,6,FIn a social media post, the area's MSP
OL,7,FFinlay Carson said: "Thanks to
OL,8,Fcontinued pressure and the concerns
OL,9,Fraised by parents, and pupils, the
OL,10,FCouncil will now provide a crossing
OL,11,Fpatrol from Monday 9th February,
OL,12,Fdelivered by their Streetscene Team.
OL,14,F"Keeping children and families safe on
OL,15,Ftheir way to and from school is
OL,16,Fabsolutely essential, and I'm glad to
OL,17,Fsee this swift action taken."
